START   LDA ZERO
        STA RESULT
        STA COUNT
        INP
        BRZ END
        STA VALUE
LOOP    LDA RESULT
        ADD VALUE
        STA RESULT
        LDA COUNT
        ADD ONE
        STA COUNT
        SUB VALUE
        BRZ ENDLOOP
        BRA LOOP
ENDLOOP LDA RESULT
        OUT
        BRA START
END     HLT
RESULT  DAT
COUNT   DAT
ONE     DAT 1
VALUE   DAT
ZERO    DAT
